Hibernate Caching:			
=====================
Caching is a mechanishm to enhance the performance of Application
Caching is used to reduce the number of databse queries
=======================
First Level Caching-> Session Object-> By Default Provide
Second Level Caching-> Session Factory-> Manually Enable
Query Level Caching
########################################
API:
====
It is a set of rules that allows program to talk to each other. The developer creates API on server side and allows client to talk to it.
##########
Rest-> representational state transfer-> stateless communication